            <p>
                Welcome to Brian Kim's humble site of learnings! The name of
                this blog is inspired by the book <a
                    href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thinking,_Fast_and_Slow"
                    >Thinking, Fast and Slow</a
                >. It specifically refers to the latter system of thinking, <strong
                    >System 2</strong
                >, which is more deliberate but slower. As a result, I take a
                moment to post anything that I find interesting, or anything
                that I have learnt.
            </p>
            <p>
